
LVEXTEND LVS PVS VGS DF -hT

vgs vgday1
lvs vgday1
df -h /mnt/lvdata

lvextend -L +1.5G /dev/vgday1/lvdata
lvs vgday1
xfs_growfs /mnt/lvdata
pvs
vgs
lvs
df -hT /mnt/lvdata

Recap

| Resize Type | Command                 |
| ----------- | ----------------------- |
| LV extend   | lvextend -L +1.5G <LV>  |
| XFS grow    | xfs_growfs <mountpoint> |
| View free   | vgs                     |


